query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(ci rt a1) NoMergeJoin(a1 ci rt t) NoMergeJoin(a1 ci rt t mc) NoMergeJoin(a1 ci mc rt t cn) NoMergeJoin(a1 ci cn mc rt t n1) */ select min(a1.name) AS writer_pseudo_name,
min(t.title) AS movie_title
from role_type AS rt
inner join cast_info AS ci
on ci.role_id = rt.id AND rt.role = 'actor'
inner join aka_name AS a1
on a1.person_id = ci.person_id
inner join title AS t
on ci.movie_id = t.id
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on t.id = mc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
inner join company_name AS cn
on mc.company_id = cn.id AND cn.country_code = '[sm]'
inner join name AS n1
on a1.person_id = n1.id AND n1.id = ci.person_id;
